<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>Imgur Gallery</title><link>https://imgur.com</link><description>description</description><lastBuildDate>2022-06-28 06:17:06.265144</lastBuildDate><item><title>My Etch A Sketch art is in the Netflix film Spiderhead!!!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/OPwgxul</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2KOV63t.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I've got 6 Etch A Sketch drawings in the Netflix movie Spiderhead! I created these drawings in November/December 2020 and have been waiting to share this news ever since.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Bv3oSdY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's surreal to see my name in movie credits. This isn't exactly the kind of film I would expect to see an Etch A Sketch in, but I am absolutely honored to pursue all-new frontier in my ridiculously niche choice of medium. It's incredible to realize that (as far as my research has shown), I am the very first Etch A Sketch artist to have their art in a bona fide movie!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/OPwgxul</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[pikajane]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>&quot;One of Those Days&quot; cartoons</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/EssZnrc</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/05Hm5Yl.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UOtUDM2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8Wc1jSQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8XDCYp7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JOyX6gk